overview:
Cygnet Infotech is a custom software development and IT solutions company founded with a goal to deliver innovative technology solutions to businesses.

We are a full service custom software development company catering complete software development life cycle with rich experience in foremost information technologies like Microsoft .Net, SharePoint, Dynamics CRM, Windows Azure, Java, PHP, Mobile, etc. We offer services like web application development, mobile application development, application integration, re-engineering & migration, software testing, web & graphic designing, business process outsourcing, IT support & services to independent software vendors, software companies and SMBs.

We help clients bridge gaps between their business and Information Technology driven goals. Since 2000, Cygnet has been providing full-cycle, high quality software development and IT solution services to client across 20 countries worldwide. Cygnet is expert in developing, customizing and integration of enterprise solutions offering a well-balanced mix of technology skills, domain knowledge, hands-on experience, effective methodology, and passion for IT.
